532
00:42:16,325 --> 00:42:19,370
Sudah kubilang, 'kan?
Kita hanya akan berkencan.

533
00:42:19,453 --> 00:42:20,538
Apa?

534
00:42:22,665 --> 00:42:24,250
Jangan terlalu menyukaiku.

535
00:42:58,200 --> 00:42:59,285
Indah sekali.

536
00:43:05,165 --> 00:43:06,000
Seo Mi-rae.

537
00:43:07,167 --> 00:43:08,002
Ya?

538
00:43:08,794 --> 00:43:09,670
Aku mengalah.

539
00:43:10,588 --> 00:43:11,422
Untuk apa?

540
00:43:12,548 --> 00:43:14,508
Kita tak perlu bertunangan.

541
