556
00:46:07,055 --> 00:46:07,890
Ada apa?

557
00:46:07,973 --> 00:46:09,016
Kenapa begini?

558
00:46:16,607 --> 00:46:17,733
Apa yang terjadi?

559
00:46:18,776 --> 00:46:19,610
Apa-apaan ini?

560
00:46:21,528 --> 00:46:25,532
<i>Seo Mi-rae, kencanmu selama 50 jam</i>
<i>dengan Choi Si-woo telah berakhir.</i>

561
00:46:25,616 --> 00:46:26,617
