562
00:46:26,700 --> 00:46:27,993
LAYANAN BERAKHIR

563
00:46:28,076 --> 00:46:29,077
Tidak!

564
00:46:30,120 --> 00:46:31,246
Choi Si-woo!

565
00:46:31,914 --> 00:46:33,081
Sial!

566
00:46:40,214 --> 00:46:41,215
Kenapa begini?

567
00:46:51,600 --> 00:46:54,561
"Kencan dengan satu karakter pria
hanya 50 jam"?

568
00:46:58,106 --> 00:46:59,066
Tidak.

569
00:47:00,567 --> 00:47:01,568
Tidak.

570
00:47:01,652 --> 00:47:03,237
Tidak!

571
00:47:04,988 --> 00:47:06,907
Besok ada rapat bersama Mipare.

572
00:47:06,990 --> 00:47:11,370
Keduanya sedang naik daun,
jadi kita harus pertahankan kontrak.

573
00:47:11,453 --> 00:47:12,621
- Baik.
- Tim 1?

574
00:47:12,704 --> 00:47:14,873
Kami sudah menghubungi Hwan-su.

575
00:47:15,624 --> 00:47:18,794
Dia ingin selesaikan serinya dulu,
jadi masih ditunda.

576
00:47:18,877 --> 00:47:21,255
<i>Choi Si-woo meninggalkan kesan mendalam.</i>

577
00:47:24,967 --> 00:47:26,260
Aduh, dingin!

578
00:47:28,929 --> 00:47:30,055
Astaga…

579
00:47:30,138 --> 00:47:32,599
<i>Hingga mengganggu hari-hariku.</i>

580
00:47:34,643 --> 00:47:36,770
<i>Fisik yang lebih realistis dari webtun,</i>

581
00:47:36,854 --> 00:47:39,606
<i>pandai berbicara, dan selalu perhatian.</i>

582
00:47:39,690 --> 00:47:41,775
<i>Semuanya berlebihan</i>…

583
00:47:53,203 --> 00:47:55,330
<i>tapi itu sisi seksinya yang kusukai.</i>

584
00:47:56,665 --> 00:47:58,208
<i>Seksi gila.</i>

585
00:47:58,250 --> 00:48:04,214
SEKSI GILA

586
00:48:04,715 --> 00:48:05,549
ULASAN LAYANAN

587
