609
00:49:19,706 --> 00:49:22,960
<i>Dia membuat hatimu meleleh.</i>

610
00:49:23,043 --> 00:49:25,087
<i>- Dia jatuh hati.</i>
<i>- Pegang tangan…</i>

611
00:49:25,170 --> 00:49:26,213
<i>Dopamin.</i>

612
00:49:27,714 --> 00:49:29,049
<i>Aku butuh dopamin!</i>

613
00:49:41,311 --> 00:49:43,814
<i>Masih ada 899 karakter lagi.</i>

614
00:49:43,897 --> 00:49:46,066
Kau yakin Si-woo paling berkesan?

615
00:49:46,775 --> 00:49:48,819
<i>Jika periode langganannya disia-siakan,</i>

616
00:49:48,902 --> 00:49:51,238
<i>kau mungkin akan menyesal.</i>

617
00:49:53,490 --> 00:49:56,118
Dia benar. Periode langgananku satu bulan,

618
00:49:56,201 --> 00:49:59,079
