628
00:51:34,216 --> 00:51:35,550
Tunggu sebentar.

629
00:51:36,301 --> 00:51:38,720
Astaga, mengesalkan sekali.

630
00:51:40,680 --> 00:51:41,515
Ayo…

631
00:51:47,687 --> 00:51:49,231
Hei, kenapa mendorongku…

632
00:52:51,877 --> 00:52:53,753
<i>Tapi, lagi-lagi Boyfriend on Demand</i>

633
